<h1 style="font-size:20px; line-height:22px; height:22px; margin-bottom:10px;">周颂·天作</h1>
<p class="source"><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?cstr=%e5%85%88%e7%a7%a6">先秦</a><span>：</span><a href="/search.aspx?value=%e4%bd%9a%e5%90%8d">佚名</a> </p>
<div class="contson" id="contsonf6f379602397">
<p>天作高山，大王荒之。彼作矣，文王康之。彼徂矣，岐有夷之行。子孙保之。</p>
</div>
</div>
